{"tid":1959530,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺啲成功人士好多都信風水/其他迷信野","createTime":"2020-04-05T12:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T17:05:31.000Z","uid":24098,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d59b630f3b80c17a6af9bb4df15c6b1cb41cfa85","tid":1959530,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"風水、塔羅、星座etc.<br />\n好多事業人生幾成功嘅人都信呢啲<br />\n令我呢個唔迷信嘅人懷疑自己<br />\n呢啲係咪就係所謂嘅<br />\n人生唔可以活得太清醒"},{"pid":"8d8b90ea833d7e9c825e48075ff6e22bd408fcb3","tid":1959530,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"龔如心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2195cd72eb13ed399db611a4949c97c2c8cffa0","tid":1959530,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8b90ea833d7e9c825e48075ff6e22bd408fcb3","tid":1959530,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"龔如心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7271a3726301b22d334cc91ec18b00492262b14","tid":1959530,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"搵地方洗下錢je"},{"pid":"012db413f471179f8a760c2ed666e535b10ff3a2","tid":1959530,"uid":276082,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"你忽略左好多失敗人士都迷信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2970fbdf8805868e193104d91951ce9afecb984","tid":1959530,"uid":199162,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"要搞清楚係因為信所以成功 定係成功咗先信"},{"pid":"2d3560144a156590a0e7d10938bd23003deda829","tid":1959530,"uid":24098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"012db413f471179f8a760c2ed666e535b10ff3a2","tid":1959530,"uid":276082,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":